{"tid":2285602,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"賭網 Betfair 仲未派彩 , 仍然接受加碼賭川普連任","createTime":"2020-11-14T08:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T09:32:18.000Z","uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bd50c047c3e46d566ab83a1e63289d85d700ceec","tid":2285602,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"美國大選前，主流民調大多傾向拜登，幾乎是8:2之比，當時坊間就有不少熟知美國民調運作的專家，認為信民調不如信賭盤，透過熱錢做「民調」，再定出自己的投資策略。<br />\n<br />\n大選後，這情況似乎又將上演。<br />\n<br />\n話說目前有不少傳媒的點票與「預測」結果都無更新，而不少「預測」結果已經定調拜登取得290張選舉人票。<br />\n<br />\n不過，當最新Real Clear Politics（RCP）更改結果，就引起掀然大波，皆因其「撤回」拜登在賓夕法尼亞勝出的結果，拜登「預測」選舉人票數減少至259票，變回低於270票以下。<br />\n<br />\n不同平台有不同取態，美聯社結果無郁過，Fox亦一樣，而Fivethirtyeight已停止更新圖表一星期，只剩live blog；當然，有右翼媒體更新截至今日的結果，特朗普仍以232張「預測」選舉人票領先拜登，Infographic內有法律爭議或重新人手點票的州份，就直接以灰色表示。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.4iOwgPmjC2pRU3p.AwSOw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MC4zMTI1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/2ef7e2d0-24b5-11eb-beda-a8accad5dd15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.4iOwgPmjC2pRU3p.AwSOw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MC4zMTI1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-11%2F2ef7e2d0-24b5-11eb-beda-a8accad5dd15&h=fdef5b93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">報道指William Hill已派彩</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n網站票數各異，原來賭盤都因為今次大選「大分裂」，賭盤如William Hill、Bet365、Betfred經已就「拜登贏」派彩（賺到笑，因為從統計資料看，整體押注特朗普較多），但全球最大網上博彩平台Betfair Exchange，與Ladbrokes等等，就仍然都未派彩。<br />\n<br />\n通常就美國大選派彩，一係根據傳媒整體Project result，和落敗一方發表的落敗演說，但今次大選特朗普陣營已明言「冇認輸呢個詞」；根據CNN日前罕有報道，指稱有人在Betfair上大額押注拜登，連本帶利71萬美元，但卻遲遲收不到錢。Betfair回應報道指，他們只會有更明確訊息哪位候選人當選，才會開始派彩。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We will only settle the markets when there is certainty around which candidate has the most projected Electoral College votes,&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n同樣未派的Coral and Betway，發言人就覺得結果未算正式，所以仲未派得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XgyFNp1rBeFRYARTWvTNkQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTI3Ny4zMDIwNTI3ODU5MjM3Ng--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/60f3c100-24b5-11eb-becd-956f74f2ffda\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXgyFNp1rBeFRYARTWvTNkQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTI3Ny4zMDIwNTI3ODU5MjM3Ng--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-11%2F60f3c100-24b5-11eb-becd-956f74f2ffda&h=4a2dc70d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國博彩市場因2020年美國總統大選而錄得史上最大政治賭盤，下注金額超過6億英鎊(約61億港元)，依目前情況來看，美國大選至少在英國賭盤層面仍未塵埃落定。之不過，網站如William Hill，已派彩不特只，仲已經有「2024年美國總統大選賭盤」（SkyBet都有），連賀錦麗（Kamala Harris）、彭斯（Mike Pence）都加入戰團呢～～"},{"pid":"4001130f843d575ff6a6de3ed26a98b3d74d5179","tid":2285602,"uid":306340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"有冇人賭佩洛西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57365de9a7dea2f7f2c0dbbf6d7f2139369f9a5a","tid":2285602,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:02:54.000Z","msg":"2024年竟然冇龐貝奧份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf9a88757c8e6297a0a9dbaadbdb2c3fb470ca9","tid":2285602,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:04:08.000Z","msg":"Mark Cuban Elon Musk 都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5991e20444865ea0d6aa543f8f5094554beb8847","tid":2285602,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4001130f843d575ff6a6de3ed26a98b3d74d5179","tid":2285602,"uid":306340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"有冇人賭佩洛西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:05:16.000Z","msg":"通殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\"